246
00:14:34,450 --> 00:14:35,080
Look.

247
00:14:35,080 --> 00:14:36,210
He borrowed 5,000 from me.

248
00:14:36,210 --> 00:14:36,970
He borrowed 3,000 from Shiquan,

249
00:14:36,970 --> 00:14:37,560
5,000 from Qi Huo,

250
00:14:37,560 --> 00:14:39,070
