271
00:15:01,200 --> 00:15:02,590
I would ask if I could.

272
00:15:02,890 --> 00:15:03,970
Gather at the training ground.

273
00:15:04,560 --> 00:15:05,570
Training!

274
00:15:05,570 --> 00:15:06,580
So annoying.

275
00:15:07,500 --> 00:15:08,590
What's wrong with you?

276
00:15:08,590 --> 00:15:09,560
You don't let me eat

277
00:15:09,560 --> 00:15:11,150
