00:38:31,190 --> 00:38:32,070
Shouldn't you and Coach Lin

871
00:38:32,070 --> 00:38:33,420
keep a low profile?

872
00:38:34,050 --> 00:38:36,060
There's nothing shameful between us.

873
00:38:36,480 --> 00:38:37,490
I know, I know.

874
00:38:37,490 --> 00:38:38,750
But I've been in this industry for so long.

875
00:38:38,750 --> 00:38:40,260
Listen to me. Keep a low profile.

876
00:38:40,260 --> 00:38:41,310
You nag too much.

877
00:38:41,310 --> 00:38:41,990
I'm leaving.

878
00:38:41,990 --> 00:38:43,330
Go ahead.

879
00:38:43,330 --> 00:38:43,790
You're so naggy.

880
00:38:43,790 --> 00:38:44,880
Nan Chu, keep it in mind.

881
00:38:45,350 --> 00:38:46,020
Go ahead.

882
00:38:47,280 --> 00:38:48,120
Oh, you.

883
00:39:05,040 --> 00:39:05,840
Sorry.

884
00:39:06,470 --> 00:39:07,190
I'm late.

885
00:39:13,400 --> 00:39:13,990
What's wrong?

886
00:39:15,880 --> 00:39:17,390
Don't break your promise again,

887
00:39:17,390 --> 00:39:18,060
got it?

888
00:39:18,530 --> 00:39:19,870
I won't.

889
00:39:24,530 --> 00:39:25,620
If I knew you were such a good actor,

890
00:39:25,620 --> 00:39:27,090
I should have let you audition.

891
00:39:29,490 --> 00:39:30,080
Really.

892
00:39:30,080 --> 00:39:31,080
It really hurts.

893
00:39:32,090 --> 00:39:32,810
What's wrong?

894
00:39:32,810 --> 00:39:34,190
I got hurt on duty.

895
00:39:35,120 --> 00:39:36,460
Are you dumb?

896
00:39:36,460 --> 00:39:37,850
Why did you pick me up when you hurt your back?

897
00:39:37,850 --> 00:39:39,060
Of course I have to pick you up.

898
00:39:39,950 --> 00:39:40,410
Let's go home.

899
00:39:43,430 --> 00:39:44,730
What? You want to drive?

900
00:40:38,950 --> 00:40:40,000
Aren't you all

901
00:40:41,260 --> 00:40:43,030
giving Instructor Lin a harder time?

902
00:40:59,370 --> 00:41:00,540
Actually,

903
00:41:01,420 --> 00:41:02,940
it's not entirely your fault.

904
00:41:03,780 --> 00:41:04,700
I don't know

905
00:41:05,410 --> 00:41:06,380
what's wrong with us all.

906
00:41:15,620 --> 00:41:16,420
Shiquan,

907
00:41:17,050 --> 00:41:17,930
what's with your attitude now?

908
00:41:17,930 --> 00:41:18,560
What are your thoughts?

909
00:41:20,570 --> 00:41:21,410
I hurt Instructor Lin

910
00:41:22,250 --> 00:41:23,050
and everyone.

911
00:41:23,470 --> 00:41:24,190
It's my fault.

912
00:41:25,950 --> 00:41:26,290
Okay.

913
00:41:27,080 --> 00:41:27,840
It already happened

914
00:41:27,840 --> 00:41:28,680
