915
00:41:29,100 --> 00:41:30,280
Let me ask you.

916
00:41:30,740 --> 00:41:32,460
Do you dare to write a joint letter with us

917
00:41:32,460 --> 00:41:33,590
to replace Lou Mingye?

918
00:41:33,890 --> 00:41:34,390
Liu,

919
00:41:35,440 --> 00:41:36,700
let Shiquan wash up first.

920
00:41:37,500 --> 00:41:39,730
Yu, stop being so wishy-washy all the time.

921
00:41:39,920 --> 00:41:41,870
It always ends in a mess.

922
00:41:42,080 --> 00:41:43,550
What do you mean?

923
00:41:43,780 --> 00:41:44,720
Everyone is tired today.

924
00:41:44,720 --> 00:41:45,610
We've had a hard day.

925
00:41:45,860 --> 00:41:46,450
Tired?

926
00:41:46,450 --> 00:41:47,370
You know it's tiring?

927
00:41:47,370 --> 00:41:48,760
It's tiring because of Lou Mingye.

928
00:41:49,090 --> 00:41:49,640
Have you forgotten

929
00:41:49,640 --> 00:41:50,350
how he treated you?

930
00:41:50,860 --> 00:41:52,240
Ever since Lou Mingye came

931
00:41:52,750 --> 00:41:53,750
and made Unit 1 and Unit 2,

932
00:41:53,750 --> 00:41:55,640
we haven't had a single good day.

933
00:41:56,270 --> 00:41:56,990
Let me ask you.

934
00:41:57,240 --> 00:41:58,460
Will you write the joint letter or not?

935
00:41:58,840 --> 00:41:59,630
Of course not.

936
00:42:00,140 --> 00:42:02,070
The thing is, this won't solve the problem.

937
00:42:02,530 --> 00:42:03,040
Okay.

938
00:42:03,790 --> 00:42:04,720
Then let's wait for Lou Mingye

939
00:42:04,720 --> 00:42:05,510
to ruin us all.

940
00:42:05,510 --> 00:42:06,560
That'll solve the problem.

941
00:42:06,770 --> 00:42:08,450
Let's be more understanding of each other.

942
00:42:08,660 --> 00:42:10,600
Besides, Lou Mingye

943
00:42:10,600 --> 00:42:12,490
doesn't have any bad intentions.

944
00:42:15,890 --> 00:42:16,770
You protect him.

945
00:42:16,770 --> 00:42:17,990
You understand him.

946
00:42:17,990 --> 00:42:18,580
I'll leave.

947
00:42:18,580 --> 00:42:19,630
You be the instructor

948
00:42:19,630 --> 00:42:20,890
and work with him.

949
00:42:20,890 --> 00:42:22,480
You can be his lackey.

950
00:42:22,480 --> 00:42:23,530
Liu Ruyi,

951
00:42:23,990 --> 00:42:25,590
